
<h2 style="margin-bottom: 2px;">Submit Options</h2>

<div style="height:15px; border-top: 1px dotted #ccc;">&nbsp;</div>

<div class="span-9" style="">
  <span style="font-size:18px; color:#7f7f7f;">Submit a Link:</span><br/>
  <% form_for(@page, :url=>"/page/") do |f| %>
    <%=h f.text_field :source_url, :placeholder=>"http://example.com/", :style=>"margin:0; margin-top:2px;" %>
    <button onclick="this.parentNode.submit()" class="btn" style="font-size: 1.6em; margin-left: 5px;"><span><span><b>&nbsp;</b><u>Submit</u></span></span></button>
    <% if f.error_messages %>
      <span style="font-size: 0.7em;">
        <%=h f.error_messages %>
      </span>
    <% end %>

  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="span-2" style="padding-top: 33px; text-align: center;">
  <span class="highlight" style="font-size:18px; font-weight:bold;">OR</span>
</div>

<div class="span-12" style="padding-left: 8px;">
  <span style="font-size:18px; color:#7f7f7f;">Upload Content:</span><br/>
  <a href="<%= page_builder_path %>" class="btn" style="font-size: 1.6em; margin-top: 5px;"><span><span><b>&nbsp;</b><u>Go To Page Builder</u></span></span></a>
</div>

<div style="height: 40px; clear:both;">&nbsp;</div>

<h2 style="margin-bottom: 2px;">Bookmarklet</h2>

<div style="height:15px; border-top: 1px dotted #ccc;">&nbsp;</div>

<div class="span-24">
  <span style="font-size:18px; color:#7f7f7f;">Drag this button into your toolbar:</span>
  <div style="clear:both; height:5px;">&nbsp;</div>
  <%= render :partial=>'/layouts/bookmarklet' %> <a href="javascript:showBookmarkletHelp();void(0);" style="font-size: 10px; color: #7f7f7f;">Help</a>
</div>

<div style="height:1px; clear:both;">&nbsp;</div>

<div id="bookmarkletHelp" style="display: none; width: 500px; position: relative; left: 75px; color: white; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); padding: 10px; border-radius: 6px; font-size:11px">
  <h2 style="color: white; width: 400px; float: left;">Bookmarklet Help</h2><div style="float:left; text-align: right; width: 100px;"><div style="padding-right: 10px; padding-top: 10px;"><a href="javascript:closeBookmarkletHelp();void(0);" style="color: white; font-weight: bold;">X</a></div></div>
  <div style="width:100%; height: 1px;clear:both;">&nbsp;</div>
  <h4 style="color:#00ccff; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom:5px;padding:0;"> What is a bookmarklet? </h4>
  <p>A bookmarklet is simply a link which performs an action when clicked. It's a small, safe tool for sharing content on <strong>TheLikeStream</strong> and cannot harm your computer or access personal information.</p>
  <h4 style="color:#00ccff; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom:5px;padding:0;"> Can I remove it later? </h4>
  <p>Yes. The bookmarklet can be "uninstalled" simply by removing the link from your bookmark toolbar or menu.</p>
  <h4 style="color:#00ccff; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom:5px;padding:0;"> I don't see my Bookmark toolbar</h4>
  <p>Some browsers don't show the bookmark toolbar by default. In this case, you can usually display the bookmark toolbar using your browser's "View" menu.</p>
  <h4 style="color:#00ccff; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom:5px;padding:0;"> Other Options </h4>
  <p style="">If you don't want to display the bookmark toolbar, you can add the bookmarklet to your bookmarks menu. You can do this by right-clicking on the button above and selecting "Add link to bookmarks." Then to share content on <strong>TheLikeStream</strong>, click it like any other bookmark.</p>
  <button onclick="closeBookmarkletHelp()" type="button" class="btn"><span><span><b>&nbsp;</b><u>Close</u></span></span></button>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8">
  function closeBookmarkletHelp(){
    $('bookmarkletHelp').hide();
  }
function showBookmarkletHelp(){
  $('bookmarkletHelp').show();
}
</script>

